  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Slice red peppers and mince garlic.",
    "In a large pan, heat vegetable oil over medium-high heat. Add sliced peppers and sauté for about 2 minutes until slightly softened.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for another minute until fragrant.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over the peppers and garlic, followed by smoked paprika. Cook for an additional 30 seconds to smoke.",
    "Reduce heat to medium and stir in passata and tomato sauce. Simmer for about 5 minutes or until slightly thickened.",
    "Stir in salt and pepper to taste. Serve hot."
